### Get the created load by ID
# @name GetLoadById
GET {{api_gateway_host}}/api/jsr385/loads/{{CreateLoad.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Authenticate.response.body.access_token}}

### Get load statistics
# @name GetLoadStats
GET {{api_gateway_host}}/api/jsr385/loads/{{CreateLoad.response.body.id}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{Authenticate.response.body.access_token}}

